{"tid":785442,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚引玉]大家試過喺老麥食過最奇怪嘅嘢係咩？","createTime":"2018-08-19T08:23:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T09:52:21.000Z","uid":193394,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"92929adceac7e2c69bfc903d4f2b367efb68027b","tid":785442,"uid":193394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T08:23:24.000Z","msg":"今日同男朋友食麥當勞<br />\n佢叫咗個板雞包餐<br />\n食食下話舊雞咁un 就吐左出嚟<br />\n點知發現係紙碎<br />\n同啲雞肉痴住<br />\n聞落仲有板燒味<br />\n可能係連埋一齊燒<br />\n我叫男朋友去換過個包<br />\n佢話唔去 費時下一個包又有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/162054_c775d1465bc3fabbd6ff81d783b74705.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F162054_c775d1465bc3fabbd6ff81d783b74705.png&h=0fb974bf&s={SIZE}\" /><del><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/162138_29d9758410f688262b8155235f463373.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F162138_29d9758410f688262b8155235f463373.png&h=738831a5&s={SIZE}\" /><del> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/19/162228_f9938a49bd68c4369b954878fc39fd08.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F19%2F162228_f9938a49bd68c4369b954878fc39fd08.png&h=2f9560b4&s={SIZE}\" /></del></del>"},{"pid":"c47b36b10bd122b5b036e1acbd72b3681ed50cea","tid":785442,"uid":132587,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T08:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2015/09/30/10/03/of-965193_960_720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.pixabay.com%2Fphoto%2F2015%2F09%2F30%2F10%2F03%2Fof-965193_960_720.jpg&h=25d002b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地大阪燒都係用呢d啦<br />\n和風板燒雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"